### Welcome route
GET http://localhost:3000/

### Get all records
GET http://localhost:3000/api/records

### Create record
POST http://localhost:3000/api/records
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Kind of Blue",
  "artist": "Miles Davis",
  "label": "Columbia",
  "genre": "Jazz",
  "releaseYear": 1959,
  "format": "LP",
  "tracks": [
    {
      "title": "So What",
      "duration": "9:22"
    }
  ],
  "pressingInfo": {
    "country": "US",
    "year": 1959,
    "color": "Black",
    "notes": "Original mono pressing"
  }
}

### Create invalid record
POST http://localhost:3000/api/records
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "",
  "artist": "Miles Davis"
}
